thread.title: BRIEF-Ascendas Real Estate Investment Trust Says 3Q FY17/18 DPU 3.97 Cents

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Ascendas Real Estate Investment Trust Says 3Q FY17/18 DPU 3.97 Cents

organizations.name: brief-ascendas real estate investment trust says

text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Ascendas Real Estate Investment Trust :
* 3Q FY17/18 DISTRIBUTION PER UNIT 3.970 CENTS * ‍QTRLY NET PROPERTY INCOME ROSE 1.7% TO S$157.6 MILLION​ * ‍Q3 GROSS REVENUE S$217.3 MILLION VERSUS S$208.6​ MILLION
* ‍PERFORMANCE FOR FY17/18 IS EXPECTED TO REMAIN STABLE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
